<HEADLINE>
URGENT: Anti-Secession Law focuses on opposing, checking secessionist activities: lawmaker
</HEADLINE>
<DATELINE>
BEIJING, March 8 (Xinhua)
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
China's enactment of the Anti-
Secession Law, as part of the overarching principle, is to closely
focus on the theme of opposing and checking the secessionist 
activities of the "Taiwan independence" forces and promoting China
's peaceful reunification, a senior Chinese lawmaker said here 
Tuesday.
</P>
</TEXT>
